videos.headline: Jenkins caps upset of Aggies with game-winning catch
videos.description: With 20 seconds remaining, LSU's Max Johnson hits Jaray Jenkins on a 28-yard pass to seal the 27-24 home victory against No. 15 Texas A&M.
